<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-519] Cant start synapse using synapse war</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-519</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when trying to start synapse using synapse.war there is a fatal massage coming synapse home is not set&lt;/p&gt;
